  <brief_title>The Role of the Fujinon Intelligent Chromo Endoscopy (FICE™) in Barrett's Esophagus</brief_title>
  <official_title>The Role of the Fujinon Intelligent Chromo Endoscopy (FICE™) for the Detection of Dysplasia in Barrett's Esophagus and in Post Ablation Barrett's Esophagus</official_title>
  <sponsors>
